                     <interp inst="t18200412-40-person411" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I believe the prisoner to be the man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18200412-40-person412">
                  ROBERT 
                  SPARROW
